Segment performance:
	‚Ä¢	Merchant (AUTO1.com): ‚Ç¨3.1bn revenue (+31%), ‚Ç¨350m gross profit (+33%), GPU ‚Ç¨976.
	‚Ä¢	Retail (Autohero): ‚Ç¨798m revenue (+35%), ‚Ç¨118m gross profit (+47%), GPU ‚Ç¨2,553 (+26%).

Operational Quality and Controls:
	‚Ä¢	The 2025 Operating Audit (July-2025) reported 99% reconciliation success between physical and system-recorded vehicles, confirming strong control over title transfer, eligibility tagging, and Borrowing-Base integrity.
	‚Ä¢	The audit also noted robust segregation of duties, fully automated VIN-level matching, and same-day settlement of sales proceeds to pledged accounts.
	‚Ä¢	No material audit exceptions or missing title documentation were observed across 537 tested samples.

